    The tags are same for ArrayList and LinkedList also. Only you have to declare the element(variable) as Arraylist / LL 

    While injecting a List type if the list has only one element then using list element in the XML Configuration is optional

Injecting Reference elements:
    <bean id="mathCheatObjectValue" class="MathCheat"/>
        <bean id="student" class="Student">
            <constructor-arg name="id" value="101"/>
            <constructor-arg name="mathCheat" ref="mathCheatObjectValue"/>
